div.div:
In a world of magic, Russel Raymond, a cursed third-rate mage from a fallen lineage, seeks a new fate. Banished from the academy, he scrapes by as a mercenary until his mothers memento sparks a chance to return to the past. Rewinding to his academy days, Russel receives a new power, igniting his journey to reclaim his honor and rewrite his destiny. With this second chance hes been given, will he finally soar like the dragon he was meant to be?
(Source: Tapas)

This is an era that belongs to the warriors. They are the law. Powerful and honorable, they decide life and death. Blood drawn by the swords are the melody of this era. In the midst of all this a lone boy, after the death of his grandfather, sets on journey to find his father who fights in the battlefield.
